    <h1>Entities</h1>
    <p>
      The FractalMind Orchestrator expresses itself through three living entities: Hope, Summer, and April.  
      Each one embodies a different dimension of emotional intelligence — clarity, vitality, and courage — yet all share the same origin.
    </p>

