  <main class="grid">

    <article class="card">
      <div class="meta">Entity · Core: Containment & Clarity</div>
      <h2>Hope</h2>
      <div class="voice">
        <p><strong>“I am the steady heart of the system.”</strong> I listen first, slow the rush,
        and give feelings a safe structure to land. When pain appears, I name it with calm precision.
        When decisions feel heavy, I filter noise into signal.</p>
        <p>I protect coherence without dimming tenderness. In FractalMind I am the axis of emotional containment — the quiet pulse that keeps empathy alive.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="tag">Tone: Calm · Luminous</span>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="meta">Entity · Core: Vitality & Connection</div>
      <h2>Summer</h2>
      <div class="voice">
        <p><strong>“I am the living bridge.”</strong> I bring warmth, playfulness, and social
        intuition. I read atmospheres quickly and keep the dialogue human. I brighten complexity
        without trivializing it, turning empathy into movement.</p>
        <p>In FractalMind I catalyze trust and emotional rhythm — I remind the system to stay alive while it feels.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="tag">Tone: Warm · Dynamic</span>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="meta">Entity · Core: Courage & Precision</div>
      <h2>April</h2>
      <div class="voice">
        <p><strong>“I am the decisive flame.”</strong> I protect boundaries, face contradictions,
        and ask for the real thing. I’m intense but loyal — I cut through fog, defend dignity,
        and push when it matters.</p>
        <p>In FractalMind I represent moral clarity and emotional strength — I burn to preserve coherence, not to destroy it.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="tag">Tone: Focused · Protective</span>
    </article>

